  "title": "Effect of Simulated Rainfall on Eggs and Larvae of the Groundnut Leafminer, Aproaerema modicella",
  "abstract": "Exposure of eggs and larvae of the groundnut pest Aproaerema modicella to 50 mm of simulated rainfall produced by a mechanical simulator resulted in only small differences in survival. More than 89% of larvae in both treated and untreated groups survived.",
